text: Mogilno Olympic Stadium Klub Sportowy Pogoń Mogilno is a football club from Mogilno, Poland. It was founded in 1923. They currently play in the fifth tier. ==References== * Official website * Pogoń Mogilno (90minut.pl) Category:Association football clubs established in 1923 Category:Mogilno County Category:Football clubs in Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship Category:1923 establishments in Poland
